text:
Winter always surprises me. When she dances she never put too much energy, never too few. She has a consistency that makes her dancing look effortless, she reminds me of Taemin sometimes. It's like she doesn't put any personal signature in her dance, but let the dance express through her body, i dont know how to explain the way i feel it, but i find this beautiful.
Other members are talented too, but my attention was catched by her
